  "detailed_description": "<h1>Another Horror Tale Games</h1><p><strong></strong><br><strong></strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Kevurah is a psychological horror game where you take on the perspective of a person organizing a funeral.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947330/extras/e6edf3e95ed201be7fc249b760f060c8.poster.avif?t=1764201757\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947330/extras/e6edf3e95ed201be7fc249b760f060c8.webm?t=1764201757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947330/extras/e6edf3e95ed201be7fc249b760f060c8.mp4?t=1764201757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Kevurah</strong><br>In Kevurah, you drive through a forest where you must reach a funeral that you must organize, bringing the various objects you have in your car into the funeral. All this while something torments and pressures you about the funeral.<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br>Kevurah is a photorealistic first-person simulator with object organization mechanics.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Atmospheric environment and photorealistic graphics<br>- Retro VHS aesthetic[/list]",
